- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the use of deep learning systems for speech processing, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing): The paper discusses the use of feature extraction and loss computation for speech processing, which falls under the domain of signal processing. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper discusses the use of neural networks for speech processing, which falls under the domain of neural computing.
